sentences: Jemina Pearl Abegg (born June 20, 1987), known by the stage name Jemina Pearl, is an American singer, and the former frontwoman of Be Your Own Pet, a punk rock band she started when she was 16.
From 2012 to 2013, she was part of a band called Ultras S/C (previously named The Black Faces) with Chetley "Cheetah" Weise and Ben Swank, which opened for The Black Belles in November 2011.
